name: Ricardo N. Gonzalez & Associates
overview:
In our personal injury cases, we will fight to make sure you get the most compensation allowed for you or your loved one’s injuries. It is very important to call an attorney BEFORE you sign any papers from the insurance companies. We will deal with the insurance companies so that you or your loved one can concentrate on getting well. We will make sure you are informed every step of the way through your personal injury claims process.

Mr. Gonzalez works for his clients to the best of his ability. He will advise them of the good points and bad points of their case. As an attorney, he has never worked for anyone else, only for his clients.
